title: The Big-Time Moves From Free Agency Week | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
The first week of free agency featured the shuffling of several high-impact fantasy players. We react to every player's new home, including DeAndre Hopkins, Stefon Diggs, Tom Brady, and others; highlight the biggest winners and losers from the week; and predict how each player's potential draft ranking for next season is affected.
Hosts: Danny Heifetz, Danny Kelly, and Craig Horlbeck
